Only for a limited range, the amounts of Mn in the composite are related to the concentrations of KMnO4 in solution (Fig. 1
                     ). Thus, the reaction of MnO4
                     − with carbon aerogel is a self-limiting reaction as previously reported [49]. GQD in the presence of KMnO4 are not stable and low amounts of KMnO4 should be used to synthesize MnOx/GQD.
